               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa nǝfq "Book of the Assistant Priest" (fols. 3ra-42rb) 
 -
                     Fǝtḥat za-wald "Absolution of the Son" (fols. 26rb-27rb).
 
 Additiones
                     1-4, colophon.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                     <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                        <locus target="#42va">42va</locus>, l.14: ተጽሕፈት፡ ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ በ፲፻ወ፱፻፷ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት፡ በወ
                        [<locus target="#42">42</locus>] ርኃ፡ መጋቢት፡ ይትባክ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘአፈጸመኒ፡ ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፈ፡
                        በዳኅና፡ ወበሰላም፡ አሜን። Written in the same hand as that of the main text. The date
                        1960 A.M. Maggābit (= February-March 1968 A.D.) is mentioned. </colophon>
                  </msItem>
                  
               </msContents>
