                     <origDate when="1968">The date 1960 A.M. Maggābit (=
                        February/March 1968 A.D.) is mentioned in the colophon. In addition,
                        Patriarch Basǝlyos (in tenure in 1959-70), Bishop Yoḥannǝs (Bishop of Tǝgray
                        in 1955-76) and King Ḫāyla Śǝllāse I (r. 1930-74) are mentioned in <locus target="#6ra">6ra</locus>.</origDate>
                  </origin>
               <provenance>Walatta Masqal (s. Additio 3). The Ms. was originally donated to the church
                     ʾOna Maʿḍo Gabra Manfas Qǝddus (s. Additio 3; cp. mss. MQM-004, MQM-010,
                     MQM-014).</provenance></history>
